<p><strong>This is more of a joke post</strong>.</p>
<h2 id="weechat-is-lightweight">Weechat is lightweight</h2>
<p>Weechat is incredible, terminal based IRC client, that I wanted to install
recently on my FreeBSD instance.</p>
<p>It&rsquo;s <u>lightweight</u>.</p>
<p>Here is log from my <code>pkg install weechat</code>:</p>
